  "body": "Hi guys, thank you for the great work you are doing on the miner! \n\nI was thinking that it would really helpful and would add a lot trust (when running a binary) if you could sign the releases, the tags and the binaries that you ship:\n- [Git Tools - Signing Your Work](https://git-scm.com/book/en/v2/Git-Tools-Signing-Your-Work)\n- [Signing tags using GPG\n  ](https://help.github.com/articles/signing-tags-using-gpg/)\n- [example to create and sign Github releases](https://wiki.debian.org/Creating%20signed%20GitHub%20releases) \n\nKeep it coming!\n",
