    "created_at": "2020-06-10T21:38:28Z",
    "updated_at": "2020-06-10T21:38:28Z",
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "I see that you have already linked the same public key between the ethereum.org download page, github, and the email address you use to identify yourself on github. Thank you @karalabe for configuring your account to sign commits you publish to github.\r\n\r\nThis is very helpful when confirming that [a commit representing a geth release has been signed and verified](https://help.github.com/en/github/authenticating-to-github/about-commit-signature-verification), and is safe to clone when building a docker image of geth for use in our production environments.\r\n\r\nPlease consider [signing all commits pushed to github](https://github.com/bitcoin-dot-org/bitcoin.org/blob/325ac4990ed7ee5e4b74cd860f02f34f3c6bceb6/docs/adding-events-release-notes-and-alerts.md#who-to-contact) as a part of your official release process. Thank you.",
